Package com.ibm.di.connector.dominoUsers

Provides classes for the Domino users connector.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDominoAction
    IDominoAction provides a common interface for classes that perfom a special Action with Domino.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DominoUsersConnector
    The Domino Users Connector enables access to and management of Lotus Domino users.
    DominoUtils
    Utility class
    UserAccess
    This class performs a user access to Domino.
    UserDeletion
    This class performs a user deletion from Domino.
    UserRegistration
    This class performs a user registration from Domino.
